values: <FONT size=2>this was a pretty great weekend. i spend it with jordan and his family at this nice rv park (oxymoron..ya moron) in thier bus that they just bought. me lace and jordan slept in the livingroom i guess and not like i dont like snugglin with lacey or anything but i couldnt sleep knowing that he was RIIGHT there and i couldnt touch him. his parents are kinda sketch on the physical contact thing and his dads not down with the word love. i guess it doesnt bother me much but i dont know.. i am really ready to be done with school but my grades are crap so what i really need is another 5 weeks of school to get them up. jazy ive been going to this girl for accupuncture and shes awsome give me a call and ill give you her number. the treatments havnt been working yet but she said it will take some time.. and oh yes much more money. well its back to fear factor for this pathetic little blonde girl.</FONT>

<FONT size=2>definitly going to the accupuncture lady today and i hate needles with a passion. but if it makes my back feel better then im all for it.. im still freaked out however. so i found out that my surgury for my tonsles is the day before jordans bday. hell of a birthday gift.. i get to go to disneyland tomorroww suckas i bet you wish you were me, cause i get to be in a fuckin wheelchair bitchess. ha, my bad back keeps me off of my feet so i get a wheelchair. but i cant go on thunder mountain the matterhorn or indiana jones. but thats ok i dont need to hurt my back anymore than it is, im just sooo excited to be going to dinseyland. haha im suuch a loser. i didnt go to star testing today which was nice, i convinced my mom that they were friggin useless so i spent the morning in a recliner with jordan sleeping and watching espn. i loved that. prom is also this weekend and its gonna be SO awsome cause i get to go with the man of my dreams bwahaha.. ok well i have to go do something TAish.</FONT>

<FONT size=1>my brother is finally back in town. he got a 2 week leave from the fort in delonega, so were thrilled to have him home. we went out to dinner the night he got in, and the fam is going the the pads game tonight. my mom got killer seats and im pretty stoked to see the new park. my other boy jordan has been with me every second i can manage, its awsome. he picked me up this morning pretty early and we went back to his house and we slept for like an hour.. soo nice, i definitly dont think school is more important that that, no matter what he says. ill most likely be there after school untill i have to go home for the game. i give it a week before he's locking his doors and closing the shades when i come over. no one can spend this much time with me and still think im cool...</FONT>

<FONT size=1>definitly had a power outage in class while i was writing my last entry so that was gay. it was super hot yesterday and i went to the islands interview and it went ok. i really hope i get that job, i need money like no other. jordans out looking for a job as well, but he gets all day to do it i have after school. he came over last night and sat around with me, its so much fun its rediculouse. im going to see him today after his TGI Fridays interview, maybe we'll head down to the beach or something, its a really nice day. im sooo damn tired tho, i cant stay awake worth a crap. oh well just another day in paradise. mandy wants to double date with jordan some night cause she has never met him, so that'll be fun. but kyle works every second of the day, which will hopefully be me soon. i just hope they'll give me prom night off if i get the job. aah i hope i get it. </FONT>

<FONT size=2>so i basically havnt written in this for like years. shall we recap.. jordan left and i prety much tryed to hide in his luggage, definitly was the hardest goodbye ever. theres good news to that sad goodbye but thats for later. i ended up catching strep and tearing my hamstring at the same time, so i quite track and went and watched the girls at celtic. at this point me lace and jordan decided i needed to go out there with her for spring break and i asked my parents and for some amazingly insain reason they said yes. thats the good part to the sad goodbye, im going out to georgia with lacey in 3 dayss!! we leave friday night at 11 fucking 50 at night. too bad i wont be able to sleep at all on the flight over. im way too excited as it is. that has pretty much been the past month or two in a nutshell. now im just fucking psuched about geeoorgia babyy. me and lace have started a secret mission to kill someone.. cant say who.. sensitive information. alright time to go find a job with megan.. hope i dont fail miserably.</FONT>

wow i had the best weekend ever. i was with jordan pretty much the whole time and i loved it. we went up to john wayne airport to pick up tommy with matt and came back and went to the wok place next to souplantation.. cant remember the name but it was really good. we ended up watching a car show at jordans for an hour or so and then we went to brendens morp bday party which was chill. jordan and i didnt stay for long tho, we headed out to run some "errands" and then we had to drive up to ontario at 12 to get his other friend who got a shitty flight. ive never been so happy just sitting in a car for and hour and a half driving in the dark. so tommy was the first to pass out with his shoes on i guess but no one really fucked with him. after we picked everyone up from brendens we went home and i had to be super sneaky to not let jordans mama know i was there. i slept in the space between his wall and bed right underneither little who i was afraid would either roll or step on me. i got up when his parents went to church and he drove me home. my mom thought i was at brookes spending the night.. little does she know... im such a bad kid, lol. on sunday i showered and went back over there at like 2 to swim and ended up staying till 8. i cant stand to think hes going back on sunday.. i love this whole him being only 10 mins away thing. well tomorrow night is our big game vs. LCC at torrey pines i found out at 6. we are gonna do so well, everyones pumped to win this whole thing. GO POWAY! lol..wierd
